Game Genre / Type: Soccer
Theme: bright colors, stadium, park

Win Condition(s): 
    -- Score 5 goals before your opponent.
Loss Condition(s):
    -- Let your opponent score 5 before you.

Levels / Screen:
    -- At a stadium.
    -- At a park.

Objectives / Enemies / Obstacles:
    -- People (home jersey, away jersey, home goalie jersey, away goalie jersey)

Items / Equipment / Objects:
    -- Power-Ups (Speed, make the player move faster.)
    -- Power-Ups (FreeBee, get a free goal.)

Difficulty Changes:
    -- adds one more opponent 
